reviewText: This product is already out there on the web in different forms.  Mostly, it's Charlie Cross yakking, video you have all seen already.  Nothing new here.

Was not what I ordered at all! The box was what it was supposed to be but the dvd inside was useless and had a different title than on the outside box. The Boy In The Bubble is an excellent documentary, what I received was not at all worth watching.
I purchased Kurt Cobain : The Boy in the Bubble, for my daughter, she is a fan and I reviewed other ratings and this helped me decide to buy.  There are many fans and his death was a loss.  RIP.
